    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Here's a fantastic opportunity to own a reliable, well-maintained vehicle that's ready to hit the road! This car presents in genuinely good condition \u2014 it's been cared for and shows only the normal, expected signs of everyday use. The mechanicals are solid, the interior is comfortable and clean, and it drives with confidence. A great value for a dependable used car \u2014 come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 as close to flawless as a used car can get. The exterior paint is brilliant and free of scratches, chips, or swirl marks, with all body panels perfectly aligned. The interior is immaculate: no stains, tears, or wear on the seats, carpets, or dashboard surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives like new \u2014 all systems are functioning perfectly, with no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises. Service history is up to date, and the tires, brakes, and fluids are all in excellent shape. This is a rare find for a buyer who wants a used car that truly feels new.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior paint is flawless, with no scratches, chips, dents, or swirl marks; it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally immaculate: all surfaces are pristine, the upholstery shows zero wear, and every button, knob, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have substantial tread remaining, the brakes are responsive, and all mechanical systems are in perfect working order. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires absolutely nothing \u2014 just get in and drive with complete confidence. A rare find for the discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than the best.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly ride you can work with? This vehicle is priced to move and offers a fantastic opportunity for the handy buyer or DIY enthusiast! We won't sugarcoat it \u2014 this car has seen better days and will need some meaningful attention and repairs to get it back in great shape. But the bones are there, and at this price, you're getting incredible value for someone willing to put in the effort. Come take a look and imagine the possibilities!",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Rarely does a pre-owned vehicle arrive in this caliber of condition. This exceptional example has been meticulously maintained from day one \u2014 every surface, system, and detail reflects the care of an owner who treated it as an investment. The exterior gleams with a flawless finish free of scratches, chips, or blemishes, while the interior presents as virtually showroom-fresh: clean stitching, spotless carpets, and fully functional electronics throughout. Service records are complete and on hand. If you've been searching for a used vehicle that drives and feels like new, your search ends here. Priced to reflect its outstanding standing \u2014 this one won't last.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I am SO excited to share this absolute gem with you today. This beauty is truly in mint condition \u2014 we're talking pristine paint that catches every ray of sunlight, an interior that smells and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor, and a mechanically sound ride that purrs like a dream. I've taken incredible care of this one, and it really shows in every single detail. Whether you're cruising downtown or hitting the open highway, this car is going to turn heads and put a smile on your face every single time. I'm the kind of seller who believes in being straight with people \u2014 what you see is genuinely what you get here, and what you get is spectacular. Don't let this one slip away; cars this clean and well-loved don't come around often. Come take her for a spin and fall in love yourself! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a true turn-key example that sets the benchmark for what a pre-owned vehicle should be. This machine rides on a fully sorted suspension geometry with zero perceptible play in the steering rack \u2014 feedback is crisp, linear, and confidence-inspiring from the first corner. The drivetrain delivers power with zero hesitation: throttle response is immediate, transmission shifts are clean and precise through every gate, and the powertrain runs at optimal thermal efficiency with no smoke, no seepage, and no compromise. Exterior panels sit flush with factory-spec tolerances, paint depth is rich and uniform under any lighting condition, and the interior surfaces show zero fatigue \u2014 stitching intact, bolsters firm, all switchgear tactile and positive. Service history is meticulous and verifiable. This is not a 'good driver' \u2014 this is a collector-grade, daily-ready specimen that will pass any pre-purchase inspection with flying colors. Serious inquiries only.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    }
  ],
